page.title: 20THE AUTHORS IN 1985.
page.content: This project has been done by two schools, Brook Street Primary, and Bishop Goodwin Junior.The work has involved using maps,guides,directories Yellow pages and books and has required us to make visits, organise walks,interview people,take photographs and make a video tape. We hope our studies are of value to you,and we are proud to put our names to this work.{Paul Cody,Joanne White, {Rosa Wallis,Claire Hansom,Jacqueline {Marlow,Lesley Carlton,Amanda Harding, {Shane Bird,Erica Halbert,Michelle {Delucchi,Gary Paterson,Katherine Van {Tilburg,Amanda Shadwick,Glenn Birkett {Lisa Thursby,Neville Bradshaw
